            "name": "Monster Core pg. 59",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "Monster Core",
          "page": 59,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "Swarms of centipedes are dangerous indeed, ravenous carpets of skittering hunger capable of devouring a traveler whole in a matter of minutes. Kobolds and mitflits are both known to incorporate swarms of centipedes into cunning traps.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
